        "release_date": "2019-05-23T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "Enjoy a great experience in virtual reality becoming a powerful magician.\n\nEnveloping, dynamic and frenetic game in which you'll have to take your wand and defend the ancient temples where the magic of the world resides.\n\nYou will have to explode orbs of energy, link orbs according to the color of their energy, send objects to another dimension, shoot magical projectiles, stop time, invoke shields ... all this and much more to save humanity from destruction.\n\nThree temples are waiting for you to defend them. In each one you will find different challenges\n\nYou can play in adventure mode or in resistance mode. In adventure mode you will have to overcome different tests in each level. In resistance mode ... ahem ... hold what you can, it will not be much\n\nWhat are you waiting for to become the magic guardian?",
